---
title: Saltimbocca Chicken & Truffle-Parmesan Mash with Asparagus & Toasted Macadamias
description: Saltimbocca is Italian for "jump in the mouth" and as soon as you taste the chicken wrapped in sage and prosciutto, you'll understand why! Add decadent sides of cheesy truffle-mashed potato and sautéed greens and you'll be jumping for joy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saltimbocca-chicken-truffle-mash-77c76c3c.jpg
